
[1]piano-forte

   PIANO-FORTE, n. [L. planus,plain, smooth; L. fortis, strong.]

   A keyed musical instrument of German origin and of the harpsichord
   kind, but smaller; so called from its softer notes or expressions. Its
   tones are produced by hammers instead of quills, like the virginal and
   spinet.
